flowchart LR
  Client[Client Query] --> Parser[Parser and Binder]
  Parser --> Optimizer[Optimizer]
  Optimizer --> Plan[Physical Plan]

  subgraph Execution[Execution Engine]
    Scan[Scan or Index Scan]
    Join[Join or Aggregate]
    Sort[Sort or Pipeline Breaker]
  end

  Plan --> Scan
  Scan --> Join
  Join --> Sort

  subgraph Storage[Storage Engine]
    Buffer[Buffer Pool]
    PageTable[Page Table]
    PageDir[Page Directory]
    Heap[(Heap or Table Pages)]
    Index[(Index Pages)]
    Temp[(Temp Spill)]
  end

  Scan --> Buffer
  Join --> Temp
  Buffer --> PageTable
  PageTable --> Heap
  PageTable --> Index
  PageDir --> Heap
  PageDir --> Index

  subgraph Recovery[Recovery Path]
    WAL[WAL or Redo Log]
    Checkpoint[Checkpoint]
    Backup[Backup and PITR]
  end

  Buffer --> WAL
  WAL --> Checkpoint
  Checkpoint --> Backup

  subgraph Concurrency[Concurrency Control]
    Locks[Locks]
    Latches[Latches]
    MVCC[MVCC Versions and GC]
  end

  Execution --> Locks
  Storage --> Latches
  Storage --> MVCC

  subgraph Observability[Required Evidence]
    PlanStats[Estimated vs Actual Rows]
    Waits[Lock and Latch Waits]
    IO[Page Reads, Writes, Fsync]
    Lag[Replica, CDC, Vacuum, Compaction Lag]
  end

  Optimizer --> PlanStats
  Locks --> Waits
  Latches --> Waits
  WAL --> IO
  MVCC --> Lag
